title: Best of The Herd for Oct 19, 2020

description:
-When things get tough Aaron Rodgers shows no fight and bails

-Baker Mayfield is the problem in Cleveland

-Tom Brady's leadership is why the Bucs had 0 penalties or turnovers against the Packers

-If you are still blaming Carson Wentz then Colin doesn't know what to tell you

-Where Colin was right, where Colin was wrong


Guest: Trent Dilfer, Super Bowl Champion
